ter-lead-chicago-film-critics-association-nominees \"Call Me By Your Name\" and \"The Shape of Water\" lead 2017 Chicago Film Critics Association Nominees] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213092421/https://chicagofilmcritics.org/blog/2017/12/10/call-me-by-your-name-and-the-shape-of-water-lead-chicago-film-critics-association-nominees |date=December 13, 2017 }}</ref><br /><ref>{{cite news|url=https://chicagofilmcritics.org/blog/2017/12/13/lady-bird-call-me-by-your-name-win-big-for-the-chicago-film-critics-association|title=\"Lady Bird,\" \"Call Me By Your Name\" win big for Chicago film critics|publisher=[[Chicago Film Critics Association]]|accessdate=December 13, 2017|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213092421/https://chicagofilmcritics.org/blog/2017/12/13/lady-bird-call-me-by-your-name-win-big-for-the-chicago-film-critics-association|archivedate=December 13, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\t\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Costume Designers Guild Awards 2017|Costume Designers Guild Awards]]\n| February 20, 2018\n| [[Costume Designers Guild Award for Excellence in Fantasy Film|Excellence in Fantasy Film]]\n| Jacqueline Durran\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2018/01/cdg-awards-nominations-costume-design-last-jedi-game-of-thrones-big-little-lies-1202239762/ |title=CDG Awards Nominations Announced For Film & TV Costuming |date=January 10, 2018 |publisher=[[Deadline (magazine)|Deadline]] |accessdate=January 10, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180110154509/http://deadline.com/2018/01/cdg-awards-nominations-costume-design-last-jedi-game-of-thrones-big-little-lies-1202239762/ |archive-date=January 10, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"4\"| [[23rd Critics' Choice Awards|Critics' Choice Movie Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| January 11, 2018\n| [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Art Direction|Best Art Direction]]\n| Sarah Greenwood and Katie Spencer\n| {{nom}}\n|