7 |archive-date=November 16, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Empire Award for Best Soundtrack|Best Soundtrack]]\n| rowspan=\"6\"| ''Beauty and the Beast''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Make-up and Hairstyling\n| {{won}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"4\"| [[Golden Trailer Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| June 6, 2017\n| Best Animation/Family\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"GTA18\">{{cite web |url=http://www.goldentrailer.com/gta-18-nominees/ |title=The 18th Annual Golden Trailer Award Nominees |work=GoldenTrailer.com |accessdate=September 6, 2017 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602080913/http://www.goldentrailer.com/gta-18-nominees/ |archivedate=June 2, 2017  }}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Original Score\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Animation/Family TV Spot\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Fantasy Adventure TV Spot\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Guild of Music Supervisors Awards]]\n| February 8, 2018\n| Best Music Supervision for Film: Budgeted Over 25 Million Dollars\n| {{sortname|Matt|Sullivan|nolink=1}}\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2018/music/news/guild-of-music-supervisors-awards-nominations-1202661480/ |title=Sufjan Stevens, 'Greatest Showman,' 'Girls' Among Guild of Music Supervisors Awards Nominees |work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]] |date=January 11, 2018 |accessdate=January 12, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113092943/http://variety.com/2018/music/news/guild-of-music-supervisors-awards-nominations-1202661480/ |archive-date=January 13, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"| [[Hollywood Film Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"| November 5, 2017\n| Costume Design Award\n| Jacqueline Durran{{efn|Also credited for ''[[Darkest Hour (film)|Darkest Hour]]''.}}\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| <ref name=\"HollywoodAwards\">{{cite web|url=http://www.goldderby.com/article/2017/hollywood-film-awards-2017-comple